t"],"pid":5867,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob:  米诺地尔就是外用药，刺激头皮血管舒张，来促进头皮毛孔生长。","timestamp":1593016160,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35900,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":5867,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"单用米诺地尔有效吗","timestamp":1593016573,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35948,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":5867,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 有效，但是据发友反馈，一旦停用米诺地尔就【有可能】复脱甚至狂脱。","timestamp":1593016869,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":35957,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":5867,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 谢谢科普！","timestamp":1593016924,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":37926,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":5867,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"都是基因决定的 坚持用药","timestamp":1593054917,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":5867,"reply":13,"tag":null,"text":"三年前自我感觉开始雄脱（androgenic alopecia），看了很多资料，去了很多次医院，吃了维生素B，锌，食物上多喝豆浆，多吃南瓜子，尽量保持好的作息。但是一直没敢吃非那雄安，也没用米诺地尔。如今看不出明显的脱发，但是额角还是越来越上了，发质也变更软了。真的好羡慕头发浓密的男生啊，能弄弄发型提升一下颜值，我就只能自惭形秽了，哭哭。","timestamp":1593015324,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782583,"url":"","vote":{}}}